stories.title: PAKISTAN v WEST INDIES
stories.subTitle: Benson & Hedges World Series Cup 1992-93, fifth match
stories.summary: After dropping five catches and missing several run-out chances, West Indies held their nerve while Pakistan panicked, losing their last seven wickets - four to run-outs - in 35 balls
